{
  "texts": [
    "Following that, a number of machine-learning models are trained and tested using the generated dataset.",
    "Table 6 shows how different models performed using PCA imputer.",
    "It demonstrates that LR and SGD results are significantly low, with accuracy rates of 69.34% and 74.17% respectively.",
    "The findings show that the accuracy for GNB, ETC, and XGBoost is 83.54%, 81.65%, and 80.19%, respectively.",
    "The findings are consistent with the prediction that using the PCA imputer enhances the outcomes since machine learning models perform better with imputing the missing values using the KNN imputer."
  ]
}